eventDescription: Join us for an exciting event focused on Keras and deep learning.
about: Keras Community Day 2023 is a gathering of deep learning enthusiasts, researchers, and practitioners. It's a day dedicated to exploring the latest advancements in Keras and deep learning technologies.
callForSpeakers: We are inviting passionate speakers to share their knowledge and insights at KCD 2023. Submit your proposal and be a part of this informative event.
